SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from :1/CLNT, :1/CMON CMON, :1/ADMN ADMN where CLNT101_ADMNO = CMON.CMON_ADMNO and CLNT102_CLNTNO = CMON.CMON_CLNTNO and CMON.CMON_CURRBALINVESTMENT <> 0 and CMON.CMON_YEAR = :2 and CMON.CMON_MONTH = :3 and CMON.CMON_CURRENCY = ADMN.ADMN_CURRENCY and CLNT101_ADMNO = ADMN.ADMN_NO and ADMN.ADMN_DELCREDERE = 'N' and ADMN.ADMN_TESTCLIENTS = 'N' and ADMN.ADMN_ENDCLIENTS = 'N' and exists (select * from :1/SCHT where SCHT_BOOKED = 'Y' and SCHT_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and SCHT_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO) and CLNT906_STATUSCONTRACT <> 2 and CLNT102_CLNTNO <> 99999 and CLNT102_CLNTNO < 20000

select CLNT101_ADMNO, CLNT102_CLNTNO, CLNT110_NAME1, CMON.CMON_CURRBALINVESTMENT, CMON.CMON_CURRBALSETTLEMENTACC, CLNT108_ACC_CURR, CLNT407_WITHRECOURSE, CLNT906_STATUSCONTRACT, CLNT614_INTERESTUPFRONT, ADMN_CURRENCY, ADMN_ADMNO_RATES from :1/CLNT, :1/CMON CMON, :1/ADMN ADMN where CLNT101_ADMNO = CMON.CMON_ADMNO and CLNT102_CLNTNO = CMON.CMON_CLNTNO and CMON.CMON_CURRBALINVESTMENT <> 0 and CMON.CMON_YEAR = :2 and CMON.CMON_MONTH = :3 and CMON.CMON_CURRENCY = ADMN.ADMN_CURRENCY and CLNT101_ADMNO = ADMN.ADMN_NO and ADMN.ADMN_DELCREDERE = 'N' and ADMN.ADMN_TESTCLIENTS = 'N' and ADMN.ADMN_ENDCLIENTS = 'N' and exists (select * from :1/SCHT where SCHT_BOOKED = 'Y' and SCHT_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and SCHT_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO) and CLNT906_STATUSCONTRACT <> 2 and CLNT102_CLNTNO <> 99999 and CLNT102_CLNTNO < 20000 and CLNT203_OFFICE = 'RO' order by CLNT.CLNT101_ADMNO, CLNT.CLNT102_CLNTNO for fetch only

SQL_STMT_U.val: select max(CDTO.CDTO_DATE) from :1/CDTO CDTO where CDTO.CDTO_CURRBALSETTLEMENTACC <= 0 and CDTO.CDTO_ADMNO = :2 and CDTO.CDTO_CLNTNO = :3 and CDTO.CDTO_DATE <= ':4'

select cast(sum (ACCC.ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/ACCC ACCC where ACCC.ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 and ACCC.ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 and Year (ACCC.ACCC_ACCT_DATE) = :4 and Month (ACCC.ACCC_ACCT_DATE) = :5 and ACCC.ACCC_MUTTYPE = 31

select cast((CSEC.CSEC701_AMOUNT * CSCC.CSCC_PERCENTAGEEXPOSURERO / 100) as decimal (13,2)), CSEC.CSEC701_CURRENCY from :1/CSEC CSEC, :1/CSCC CSCC where CSCC.CSCC_TYPE = CSEC.CSEC701_TYPE and CSEC.CSEC_ADMNO = :2 and CSEC.CSEC_CLNTNO = :3 and CSCC.CSCC_PERCENTAGEEXPOSURERO > 0

select cast(sum (DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/DEBB DEBB, :1/DEBC DEBC where DEBB.DEBB_ADMNO = :2 and DEBB.DEBB_CLNTNO = :3 and DEBC.DEBC_NO = DEBB.DEBB_DEBC_NO and DEBB.DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH > 0 and DEBC.DEBC_CREDITLIMITH > 0
